-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Making an image fill entire background:

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;

THEN alter HTML

html{
height:100%;
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Navs automatically have flexbox components
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To get bootstrap cards the same size:

set img class="card-img-top"

THEN alter CSS

.card-img-top {
    width: 100%;
    height: 15vw;
    object-fit: cover;
}
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
